<br>
anyway this leads me to the purpose of this post. i would like to see a true roleplay server enacted. one that followed the ruleset of the OLD fv  but even moreso. a server where you could not group with differing alignments (other then neutral) at ALL. one where p vs p was a reality from level 1  and once you died... you were dead for good. Finally (and most importantly) a server that was confined to  simply the original version of everquest (maybe kunark so people could play lizardmen and open up the other dragons ) to play eq as it was ment to be played.. as a true roleplaying game where those who had a love for RP could get together  and live out the fantasy. <br>
<br>
then again this is just the ramblings of an old paladin who grows more tired with each passing day.. and has trouble remembering those once close to him......<br>
<br>
Liam Holyblade<br>
Paladin of Mithaniel<br>
Proud wielder of Soulfire<br>
